<br>
Run them around so they are all bunched up.<br>
Use Atol's or BoF if you fizzle Atol's too much. <br>
Cast snare and hope it sticks on all.<br>
IF IT STICKS...<br>
run around casting your AoE on them all until they die, resnare if needed.<br>
<br>
IF IT DOESNT STICK...<br>
run the ones that didn't stick around but make sure you are still in the agro range of the ones it did stick. Cast snare as fast as you can and get the ones snared! Then run in between them for a bit (in between the 2 groups of snared ones) until they group up. Resnare because it should run off the first group soon. Then run around casting your AoE on them all until they die, resnare if needed. <p>Oltovillo Miniime<br>
